      <title>渣打银行在英国就 Libor 替代利率的诉讼中取得部分胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-partially-wins-uk-court-case-over-replacement-rate-libor-2024-10-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行周二在伦敦一家法院赢得了诉讼，成功更换了用于设定部分股票股息利率的金融基准，这是一起早期有关摆脱伦敦银行间拆借利率 (Libor) 的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-partially-wins-uk-court-case-over-replacement-rate-libor-2024-10-15/</guid>
